findings.subquery: Biographical details of Tarun Manohar Jaswani
key_findings: Tarun Manohar Jaswani is an Indian businessperson born on June 27, 1977, in Delhi, India. ([wikidata.org](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q109470450?utm_source=openai))
He is the son of Manohar Khemchand Jaswani, a fellow entrepreneur. ([wikidata.org](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q109470450?utm_source=openai))

Tarun holds a Bachelor of Technology degree from the Department of Technology at Savitribai Phule Pune University, completed between 1995 and 1999. ([aeroleads.com](https://aeroleads.com/in/tmjaswani?utm_source=openai))
He is the founder and Chief Executive Officer of Unbound Finance, a company specializing in financial software. ([pitchbook.com](https://pitchbook.com/profiles/person/263211-85P?utm_source=openai))

Previously, he co-founded Ring India Infotech Private Limited in 2000 and Interfacemax Contacts Private Limited in 2001. ([thecompanycheck.com](https://www.thecompanycheck.com/people-profile/tarun-jaswani/00084725?utm_source=openai))

Tarun has also been associated with Maravilloso Realtors Private Limited, serving as an additional director over 10 years ago. ([quickcompany.in](https://www.quickcompany.in/company/maravilloso-realtors-private-limited?utm_source=openai))
